OL,3,CHow will social media ban for under-
OL,4,C16s work and which apps are affected?
OL,6,FPrime MinisterKeir Starmer has
OL,7,Fannounced a sweeping ban on social
OL,8,Fmedia for under-16s that is set to
OL,9,Fbegin next year.
OL,11,FSpeaking at a press conference on
OL,12,FMonday, the prime minister said the
OL,13,Fmove would protect children, who are
OL,14,Foften exposed to "harmful content" or
OL,15,Fbullies who "harass and abuse" others
OL,16,Fonline.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
