OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781539876
OL,3,CHow will social media ban for under-
OL,4,C16s work and which apps are affected?
OL,6,FThe PM also said there was an
OL,7,F"opportunity cost" due to the
OL,8,Faddictiveness of social media, which
OL,9,F"stops children doing their homework,
OL,10,Freading, playing with their friends
OL,11,Foutside, going to bed a decent hour".
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,F"I come to it as a parent myself. I
OL,19,Fknow exactly the fears that we all
OL,20,Ffeel when we're thinking about this
OL,21,Fissue," Starmer said.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
