OL,3,CHow will social media ban for under-
OL,4,C16s work and which apps are affected?
OL,6,FThe government has said it plans to
OL,7,Fuse the same model as the recent
OL,8,Fsocial media ban in Australia, which
OL,9,Fcame into effect in December last year.
OL,11,FHere's everything you need to know.
OL,13,FHow will a ban work?
OL,15,FThe exact details of the ban are not
OL,16,Fyet clear, but the government has said
OL,17,Fit intends to follow legislation in
OL,18,FAustralia and even go further in some
OL,19,Fareas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
