OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781539876
OL,3,CHow will social media ban for under-
OL,4,C16s work and which apps are affected?
OL,6,FIt will be down to social media
OL,7,Fplatforms to ensure their users are
OL,8,Fover the age of 16, meaning children
OL,9,For parents won't encounter penalties
OL,10,Fif they break the law, Starmer said.
OL,12,FIn Australia, platforms can face huge
OL,13,Ffines of up to 49.5 million Australian
OL,14,Fdollars (around #25 million) if they
OL,15,Fdon't take "reasonable steps" to
OL,16,Fprevent under-16s from having accounts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
