OL,3,CHow will social media ban for under-
OL,4,C16s work and which apps are affected?
OL,6,FThis can include asking for ID, having
OL,7,Fface or voice recognition, or so-
OL,8,Fcalled "age inference" tech, which
OL,9,Fanalyses users' behaviour and
OL,10,Festimates their age.
OL,12,FOfcom will conduct a study on what is
OL,13,Fthe most effective age assurance for
OL,14,Fverifying whether someone is over 16,
OL,15,Fthe government said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
