OL,3,CHow will social media ban for under-
OL,4,C16s work and which apps are affected?
OL,6,FThe ban will also include "world-
OL,7,Fleading" blocks on "harmful
OL,8,Ffunctions", such as livestreaming and
OL,9,Fcommunicating with strangers, for
OL,10,Funder-16s on other online services,
OL,11,Fincluding gaming sites.
OL,13,FThese restrictions, together with the
OL,14,Fban, "go further than any other
OL,15,Fcountry", the government said.
OL,17,FFamily accounts, created by parents
OL,18,Fbut featuring children, will not be
OL,19,Faffected by the ban, Starmer told
OL,20,Fjournalists.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
