OL,3,CHow will social media ban for under-
OL,4,C16s work and which apps are affected?
OL,6,FWhich platforms will be affected?
OL,8,FSnapchat, TikTok, YouTube, Instagram,
OL,9,FFacebook and X are all included in the
OL,10,Fban, the government said.
OL,12,FThreads, Twitch, Kick, BlueSky, Lemon8
OL,13,Fand Reddit are also likely to be
OL,14,Fblocked for under-16s, as per the
OL,15,Frules in Australia.
OL,17,FThe government has said the ban will
OL,18,Fnot involve messaging services, like
OL,19,FWhatsApp and Signal, and Australia
OL,20,Falso permits the use of sites like
OL,21,FMessenger, Roblox and YouTube Kids.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
