OL,3,CHow will social media ban for under-
OL,4,C16s work and which apps are affected?
OL,6,FWhat about 16 and 17-year-olds' social
OL,7,Fmedia use?
OL,9,FWhile those above the age of 16 will
OL,10,Fbe able to have social media accounts,
OL,11,Frestrictions on functionalities such
OL,12,Fas livestreaming and talking with
OL,13,Fstrangers will also apply to under-
OL,14,F18s, the government said.
OL,16,FMore detail on overnight curfews -
OL,17,Frestrictions on social media use at
OL,18,Fnight - and breaks in infinite
OL,19,Fscrolling for under-18-year-olds will
OL,20,Falso be set out in July.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
