OL,3,CHow will social media ban for under-
OL,4,C16s work and which apps are affected?
OL,6,FSo-called AI "romantic companion"
OL,7,Fchatbots, designed to simulate sexual
OL,8,Frelationships or roleplay with users,
OL,9,For similar functions on other
OL,10,Fchatbots, will also have to enforce a
OL,11,Fminimum age of 18.
OL,13,FEarlier this month, the UK asked tech
OL,14,Fcompanies, including Apple and Google,
OL,15,Fto make it impossible for children to
OL,16,Ftake, share, or view nude images on
OL,17,Ftheir platforms, and they have a three-
OL,18,Fmonth deadline to comply.
OL,20,FWhen will the social media ban come
OL,21,Finto force?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
