OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781539876
OL,3,CHow will social media ban for under-
OL,4,C16s work and which apps are affected?
OL,6,FThe ban is expected to be brought to
OL,7,Fparliament before Christmas, the
OL,8,Fgovernment said.
OL,10,FThe protections should then come into
OL,11,Fforce by spring 2027.
OL,13,FWhat impact has Australia's ban had?
OL,15,FAround 4.7 million underage accounts
OL,16,Fwere removed or restricted from
OL,17,Fplatforms during the first month of
OL,18,Fthe ban in Australia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
