OL,3,CHow will social media ban for under-
OL,4,C16s work and which apps are affected?
OL,6,FSome children were also able to edit
OL,7,Ftheir ages to be above 16 or
OL,8,Fsuccessfully bypass facial age
OL,9,Festimation when the platforms notified
OL,10,Fthem of the ban.
OL,12,FThere are five ongoing investigations
OL,13,Finto potential non-compliance across
OL,14,FFacebook, Instagram, Snapchat, TikTok
OL,15,Fand Youtube, the report said, with the
OL,16,Foutcomes expected in the coming weeks.
